        <p class="!mb-0 !text-sm text-mist italic">
          I wrote this a week into using <a href="https://openclaw.ai">OpenClaw</a>, the open-source AI agent that became the foundation for everything I've built since. It was originally just me processing my own thoughts — trying to make sense of what I was experiencing and why it felt different. The ideas here became the seed of what eventually grew into <a href="/">Ouroboros</a>.
        </p>
